    "collapsible_content_4xBrM4": {
      "type": "collapsible-content",
      "blocks": {
        "block_87tc79": {
          "type": "block",
          "settings": {
            "title": "What is Breathelet?",
            "content": "<p>Breathelet is a wearable mindfulness bracelet that gives gentle vibration reminders at random moments throughout the day. Each reminder is designed to help you pause, check in with yourself, and return to the present moment.</p>",
            "content_from_page": "",
            "open": false,
            "heading_html_tag": "p"
          }
        },
        "block_DieqKi": {
          "type": "block",
          "settings": {
            "title": "How does Breathelet work?",
            "content": "<p>Breathelet gently vibrates at random intervals during the day typically every 60–150 minutes, making each reminder feel natural rather than scheduled. When you feel the vibration, use it as a simple prompt to pause, breathe naturally, notice how you feel, or take a mindful moment before continuing your day.</p>",
            "content_from_page": "",
            "open": false,
            "heading_html_tag": "p"
          }
        },
        "block_bxnqB4": {
          "type": "block",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Why are the reminders random?",
            "content": "<p>The random timing is intentional. When reminders happen on a fixed schedule, they can become predictable and easier to ignore. Random reminders feel more natural and help each vibration stay noticeable as a mindful pause prompt.</p>",
            "content_from_page": "",
            "open": false,
            "heading_html_tag": "p"
          }
        },
        "block_Uf6iyX": {
          "type": "block",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Is Breathelet a breathing exercise timer?",
            "content": "<p>No. Breathelet is not designed to make you follow breathing exercises on a fixed schedule. It is designed to gently remind you to pause, check in, and reconnect with yourself throughout the day.</p>",
            "content_from_page": "",
            "open": false,
            "heading_html_tag": "p"
          }
        },
        "block_QVfyQ6": {
          "type": "block",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Who is Breathelet for?",
            "content": "<p>Breathelet is for anyone who wants a simple, screen-free reminder to slow down and be more present during daily life. It can be used at work, while studying, commuting, relaxing, or moving through a busy day.</p>",
            "content_from_page": "",
            "open": false,
            "heading_html_tag": "p"
          }
        },
        "block_fi7fkX": {
          "type": "block",
          "settings": {
            "title": "What can I use each reminder for?",
            "content": "<p>You can use each gentle vibration as a reminder to:</p><ul><li>Pause for a moment</li><li>Check in with yourself</li><li>Take a natural breath</li><li>Notice your thoughts or emotions</li><li>Practice gratitude</li><li>Drink water</li><li>Reset your focus</li><li>Return to the present moment</li></ul>",
            "content_from_page": "",
            "open": false,
            "heading_html_tag": "p"
          }
        },
        "block_KXiXhW": {
          "type": "block",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Can Breathelet help with anxiety, stress, or medical conditions?",
            "content": "<p>Breathelet is not a medical device and is not intended to diagnose, treat, cure, or prevent any health condition. It is designed as a simple mindfulness reminder to support mindful pauses and daily awareness.</p>",
            "content_from_page": "",
            "open": false,
            "heading_html_tag": "p"
          }
        },
        "block_QUcWXm": {
          "type": "block",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Does Breathelet require an app?",
            "content": "<p>No. Breathelet does not require an app, Bluetooth, or phone setup. It is made to work independently, so you can use it without adding another screen or notification to your day.</p>",
            "content_from_page": "",
            "open": false,
            "heading_html_tag": "p"
          }
        },
        "block_BBUGBc": {
          "type": "block",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Does Breathelet have a screen?",
            "content": "<p>No. Breathelet has no screen and no distracting display. It is designed to feel like a simple bracelet while giving gentle vibration reminders throughout the day.</p>",
            "content_from_page": "",
            "open": false,
            "heading_html_tag": "p"
          }
        },
        "block_A3hmAH": {
          "type": "block",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Is Breathelet waterproof?",
            "content": "<p>Breathelet is water-resistant, not fully waterproof. It can handle everyday splashes, light moisture, and daily wear, but it should not be worn while swimming, showering, or fully submerged in water.</p>",
            "content_from_page": "",
            "open": false,
            "heading_html_tag": "p"
          }
        },
        "block_Lc9fBL": {
          "type": "block",
          "settings": {
            "title": "How long does the battery last?",
            "content": "<p>Breathelet is designed with a long-lasting battery that can last up to 14 days, depending on usage and charging habits.</p>",
            "content_from_page": "",
            "open": false,
            "heading_html_tag": "p"
          }
        },
        "block_Dqcnwc": {
          "type": "block",
          "settings": {
            "title": "How do I charge Breathelet?",
            "content": "<p>Charge Breathelet using the provided charging accessory or compatible charging setup included with your order. For best performance, keep the charging area clean and dry before charging.</p>",
            "content_from_page": "",
            "open": false,
            "heading_html_tag": "p"
          }
        }
      },
