        "content": "<p>Breathelet is a simple, screen-free bracelet designed to help you pause, check in with yourself, and take mindful moments throughout the day. Its gentle random vibrations act as subtle reminders to slow down, reconnect, and build better daily awareness without using an app, screen, or fixed schedule.</p>",
