        "block_nwtCQx": {
          "type": "block",
          "settings": {
            "title": "How should I wear my Breathelet?",
            "content": "<p>Wear Breathelet snug against your wrist, not loose. The bracelet should stay close enough to your skin so you can feel the vibration, while still feeling comfortable for daily wear.</p>",
            "content_from_page": "",
            "open": false,
            "heading_html_tag": "p"
          }
        },
        "block_bmnBwi": {
          "type": "block",
          "settings": {
            "title": "What is the ideal fit?",
            "content": "<p>The ideal fit is: secure and stable on your wrist, comfortably snug without restricting movement, close enough to feel each vibration clearly, and not sliding, spinning, or hanging away from your wrist.</p>",
            "content_from_page": "",
            "open": false,
            "heading_html_tag": "p"
          }
        },
        "block_ebYcL7": {
          "type": "block",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Why am I not feeling the vibration?",
            "content": "<p>This is usually caused by a loose fit. Make sure Breathelet is worn snug against your wrist and positioned close to your skin. If it moves around too much, the vibration may feel weaker.</p>",
            "content_from_page": "",
            "open": false,
            "heading_html_tag": "p"
          }
        },
        "block_CWNcbt": {
          "type": "block",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Can I adjust the size?",
            "content": "<p>Yes. Breathelet features an adjustable string design so you can set it to your preferred fit. Pull the strings to adjust the size, trim extra length if needed, and use the hook closure for easy everyday wear.</p>",
            "content_from_page": "",
            "open": false,
            "heading_html_tag": "p"
          }
        },
        "block_WCEwpV": {
          "type": "block",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Can I wear Breathelet all day?",
            "content": "<p>Yes. Breathelet is designed for daily wear. For comfort and care, remove it before showering, swimming, or exposing it to extreme moisture.</p>",
            "content_from_page": "",
            "open": false,
            "heading_html_tag": "p"
          }
        },
        "block_AQXjwY": {
          "type": "block",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Which wrist should I wear it on?",
            "content": "<p>You can wear Breathelet on either wrist. Choose the side that feels most comfortable and makes it easy for you to notice the gentle vibration.</p>",
            "content_from_page": "",
            "open": false,
            "heading_html_tag": "p"
          }
        }
